<br>
   I congratulate him on mastering the use of the /who command. However, it should be obvious to you that I have to go recover my own body.<br>
<br>
    Then he asks again...<br>
  <br>
    /bonk annoying_bard<br>
<br>
    Repeat question<br>
<br>
    /bonk annoying_bard<br>
<br>
    Me: I'm on my way to get my own corpse.<br>
<br>
    Annoying_Bard:  So you don't have time to tp me then?<br>
<br>
    Me: &quot;There are two infinite things, the Universe and human stupidity, and I'm not sure about the Universe. -Albert Einstein.&quot;<br>
<br>
    Annoying_Bard: So you're stupid then.<br>
<br>
    Me: Yes I am, but not quite as dumb as someone who assumes I'm going to take the time out to teleport them before making my own corpse run.<br>
   <br>
    Then I proceed to make my corpse run.<br>
   (Okay, so the last was  two lines were out of hand.) It didn't help that the bard's name was Tutifruiti either.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=zarek>Zarek</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/20/01 1:10:14 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What is with some people? Yet another Taxi Rant...</span><hr size=1> It comes down to this. The majority of the people that play everquest are stupid, selfish, or both. They only care about themselves. Its totally out of hand. I get teleport requests from people asking me for teleports just like all of the other wizards out there. But these people somehow think that it is our duty to inconvenience ourselves to save them some time. My personal favorite request for teleport was this. I was in Greater Faydark. A person in Highpass hold sent me a tell asking me to teleport him to the West Commons. I immediately flipped out. I said, let me get this straight, you want me to teleport myself to west commons or north karana, run to highpass to get you, and then teleport you to west commons i.e. you want me to do the running for you. People are inconsiderate and its not going to change. <br>
<br>
Back to the topic thats on most of our minds, the wizards need to get a bone thrown to them from Verant very soon. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uqaman.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qaman</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/20/01 1:17:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What is with some people? Yet another Taxi Rant...</span><hr size=1> Hehe, I was on the docks in Oasis waitin on the raft to head out to TD the other day when some guy sends me a tell asking me to port him to DL. Told him no because it would take too long and I was waitin to head out to TD. So he sends back that I could bind there and port him. I told him it costs 5k to bind in Oasis. He said it does not, and I told him it does if wants me to do it for him. Anyways.. what is with these kinds of people? I am not going to change my bind spot just so I can give them a ride. Even after the push ports go live we are still going to get the same thing from people who don't want to go where the ports we got do. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utargonis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Targonis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/20/01 1:36:47 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What is with some people? Yet another Taxi Rant...</span><hr size=1> I have another check-list item you might want to add.  I will normally refuse to port any but my friends when I'm busy or not in the mood to port, but IF the person who asks me belongs to a guild I respect, then I may do it anyway.  A wizard from Eastern Legends guild on Nameless once did me an amazing favor and did the research for me for ALL my level 49 research spells without my even asking him(I was asking for runes for gravity flux back then when I was level 44).  He even provided most of the runes, and didn't charge me a dime.  Needless to say, I would NEVER accept even a donation from someone in Eastern Legends after that, even though level 49 was a long time ago now(I'm level 55).<br>
 <p>Targonis Manastorm<br>
Level 55 Wizard<br>
Call of Ascension<br>
The Nameless Server<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unaanaaneebooboo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Naanaan Eebooboo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/26/01 5:22:46 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What is with some people? Yet another Taxi Rant...</span><hr size=1> Do what I do. If someone gives me a tell and asks for a port somewhere, and refuse to take 'no' as an answer, I tell them &quot;yeah sure I'll port ya. Be there in abit&quot;.<br>
<br>
After 5-10 minutes have elapsed, I normally get another tell asking if I was coming.<br>
<br>
I'll say, &quot;yeah got held up abit. Be right there&quot;. Be creative and think up excuses for every subsequent tell you get. It's fun to see just how dumb some people are.<br>
<br>
My record so far is 30 minutes. The guy wanted me to run to Qeynos, pick his ass up, and port him to NK. He says &quot;u&quot; instead of &quot;you&quot;, &quot;plz&quot; instead of &quot;please&quot;, and didn't seem to care that the nearest port I have is to WK. I don't care if you think I'm being petty... if you want me to waste my time porting your ass, you'd better take the effort to actually spell your words properly. At the end of the 30 minutes, when he finally wisened up and flooded me with &quot;FU d00d! I hope you die IRL!&quot;s (earning a spot in my ignore list), I did a /who and found out that he was still sitting in Qeynos. <br>
<br>
Made my day.<br>
<br>
Best thing is, you can't be banned for this.<br>
<br>
Disclaimer: I don't do this often. Only to the really irritating port beggars who keep flooding me with requests, and basically insinuating that their time is worth more than mine. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufilanfyretracker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Filan Fyretracker</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/27/01 11:22:34 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/filanwizard/pic01.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What is with some people? Yet another Taxi Rant...</span><hr size=1> we should all stop using common and ack like NYC taxi drivers they still get fares dont they. <p><center><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/filanwizard/fizeau12.jpg><b><font color="#3333FF"><font size=+2><a href="mailto:filan@snet.net">Filan
